        <mxCell id="wf-release-manual" value="&lt;b&gt;release-manual.yml&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:9px;&quot;&gt;[Release] Manual Version Release&lt;br&gt;Trigger: workflow_dispatch (input: version e.g. 0.3.0)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Job 1: &lt;b&gt;commit-release&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;  → uses: update-version-files (action)&lt;br&gt;  → git tag x.y.z + push&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Job 2: &lt;b&gt;publish-and-trigger-ci&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;  → gh release create (draft)&lt;br&gt;  → gh workflow run × 7 CI workflows&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontFamily=SFMono-Regular;fontSize=10;html=1;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="350" y="520" width="260" height="175" as="geometry" />
